  <li>Enable automatic security updates if supported</li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ufw</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">fail2ban</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">apt</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">unattended-upgrades</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">systemctl</code></li>
